highlights.text: Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Manchild” is the highest at #13.
“Vanavond (Uit M'n Bol)” by Kris Kross Amsterdam, Donnie, and Tino Martin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 61 spots at #127.
“Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 646 days straight.
